## Job__c Fields
| Field Label | API Name | Type | Required |
|-------------|----------|------|----------|
| Job Title | `Job_Title__c` | Text(100) | Yes |
| Department | `Department__c` | Picklist (Engineering, Sales, HR, Finance) | Yes |
| Location | `Location__c` | Text(80) | No |
| Job Description | `Job_Description__c` | Long Text Area(32768) | No |
| Required Skills | `Required_Skills__c` | Long Text Area(5000) | No |
| Min Salary | `Min_Salary__c` | Currency(10,2) | No |
| Max Salary | `Max_Salary__c` | Currency(10,2) | No |
| Status | `Status__c` | Picklist (Draft, Open, Closed) | Yes |
| Posting Date | `Posting_Date__c` | Date | No |

